{"tid":1802181,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"上海至雅見工俾人呃","createTime":"2019-12-29T09:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T04:00:30.000Z","uid":329526,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c7da3a0d7cdca610c8ce754de8ca78e59d3ab1ed","tid":1802181,"uid":329526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"請廣傳!!!!!不能再容忍呢班垃圾呃港人錢!!<br />\n呃人見工!!實際上拉人頭加層壓式推銷!!<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5Advaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5Advaf.png&h=50d72c5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBgTvah.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBgTvah.png&h=71b6cdc1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5yWL5JE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5yWL5JE.png&h=0a9dd4b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZv1D3G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZv1D3G.png&h=5cb5c250&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVkH7W4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVkH7W4.png&h=5efcde8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44CvxoO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44CvxoO.png&h=9a0a5638&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WJq5JQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WJq5JQ.png&h=327f0d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRr4BQw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRr4BQw.jpg&h=6d4c73dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n垃圾 #海至雅生物科技有限公司<br />\n呃人上嚟見工，實際上就 #拉人頭，逼你上去俾 #$16800話乜春做 #基因測試，測12樣代謝，然後加入佢哋做犯法野(#層壓式推銷)，氹啲冇乜返工經驗嘅人上去做，氹你俾錢，話咩如果您自己要向人哋sale呢一樣野，你自己就要做左先，到sale嘅時候先有說服力喎。話俾錢買個機會，sale足個幾兩個鐘，唔俾錢走唔到禁濟，您睇手機佢又𥄫您手機，您搵袋佢又𥄫袋，時不時仲係禁拍您磗頭，簡直恐嚇。出面做基因測試幾千蚊測幾百樣野，佢哋成皮野測得戈12樣。見佢哋上完東張西望同蘋果仲係fb各大搵工群度釣水魚，見到都嬲。<br />\n依家佢哋唔敢同人哋講自己做基因，呃鳩人話咩做 #幼兒行業、話係 #合作 之類，總之佢哋一定會呃您見工戈啲，見到係 #尖沙咀 就記得好走。 <br />\n1402室, 金壘商業中心26-28號 Cameron Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui (佢哋10樓都有office)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v83vk7De5sg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv83vk7De5sg&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9wu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=afd11c3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v83vk7De5sg</a>"},{"pid":"542fe7fc493e327da434fa5691dfae41c48f23fb","tid":1802181,"uid":303269,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"認得佢地 成日呃人上去見工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ce78dbf3b9803b5475f1e288bdf31ff5641934","tid":1802181,"uid":303269,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"大疊錢影出黎 究竟有冇報稅呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e34f0ce1daee22f71ac213c4b47a5823ef977b","tid":1802181,"uid":303269,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"原來香港仲要咁荀既工 叫人上黎比錢 就有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c0cf757e913d9612c5365148d7f5d54b034a83","tid":1802181,"uid":303269,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"好似一上去就中伏 千其唔好上去八卦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc915fbc581b9425617de8a33a4d84cca49858bb","tid":1802181,"uid":189099,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"唔係串樓主你 <br />\n雖然你條氣實係好唔順<br />\n但當交學費啦 買個教訓啦<br />\n<br />\n不過呢間野係8月已經上過蘋果一次<br />\n所以勸樓主都睇多d其他新聞<br />\n<br />\n利申：有個fd係7月比呢間撚屌野昆"},{"pid":"e1aae6589cddf26a6a8faf693637a9bfcf81f947","tid":1802181,"uid":128102,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"呢d真係有少少覺得唔對路即走<br />\n<br />\n之前試過成班人上堂俾d導師洗左成兩個鐘腦<br />\n好啦講講下又陰d陰d話有少少收費<br />\n聽到我就去廁所之後頭也不回<br />\n班on9仲好興奮咁okok<br />\n最後